{
  "stem": "8423.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then when I saw that look on his face, I just kind of jumped up and into the-- into the little lookout tower, because I was hanging out.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I somehow pushed myself, I guess, on my hip to turn around, and I gave him a shove.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I started running down the stairs, but I fell.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I must have hit a rock, because I knocked out one of my tooth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I didn't know it at that time, but I saw blood coming from my mouth, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you think I run back?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I waited for the dishes, because I was afraid to come back for-- you know, without the dishes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've waited for the dishes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when I got to the gate, and the other two guys at the gate, the two guards saw me bleeding and everything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And oh, and I was all, you know, scuffed and bleeding.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My uniform was torn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They got a kind of kick out of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They kind of like laughed, you know, like what happened to her?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, that kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they let me through the gate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the two older women who were the chefs, who were women from among us-- as a matter of fact, Frau Rubencheck and Frau Hoffman were two older women who figured out right away-- they each had a daughter with my age-- that if we are this many people at the camp-- you see, you have to be older and experienced to think properly-- that they'll probably need chefs.",
      "word_count": 69
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, there were no more chefs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One of them was a famous opera star, Marta Hoffman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she always sang opera in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Germans loved it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
